::Firaxis/Horn::
       Firaxis smiles down at his completed companion.  "It's done."  He hits 
a few keys to activate the bot lying on the table.  "Come with me Horn, it's 
time to meet our comrades."  Horn nods and gets off of the table in his dog 
mode.  Together they walk into the Autobot ship and wait on the bridge.

--part1_94.24f00918.29f02ca9_boundary
